name: ContestDesigns.com
overview:
Who we are

ContestDesigns is a new startup that helps to connect individuals, entrepreneurs, start-ups, small, medium and big companies and organizations to a community of experienced, skilled, multi-talented, and diverse group of designers. We felt there shouldn’t be any boundary in reaching out to the best designers in the world or perhaps getting the best possible design for your design needs. That’s why we started ContestDesigns to help make getting the best designs whether it is making a new website or revamping a webpage, starting a business blog, rebranding a company, making a new logo, getting a new design for your business stationery supplies or just want a set of web icons or graphic images to enhance your website. At ContestDesigns all of that can be achieved without wasting time.

Our goal

Our goal is to make it easy for anyone from anywhere in the world to have access to the best designers or work on high-end design projects that pay a lot while also building reputation for the designers. We are as focused as anything possible, and we want to change the design world!

Where we are

ContestDesigns is located in Newark, New Jersey - a great city for our great dream. With the entrepreneural atmosphere here, we are certain we will evolve to be the premiere go-to-place for anything design.
